 therein). Since the first version of our monograph was circulated,\napplications of our results have appeared in the proof of Property P for knots\nby Kronheimer and Mrowka [arXiv:math/0311489] and work of Sivek on Donaldson\ninvariants for symplectic four-manifolds [arXiv:1301.0377].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2002 23:40:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 11:22:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 May 2018 22:25:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Dec 2018 22:46:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-31"}
